description:
An animated scrolling retro grid effect

Add the following animations to your tailwind.config.js file:
extend: {
      animation: {
        grid: "grid 15s linear infinite",
      },
      keyframes: {
        grid: {
          "0%": { transform: "translateY(-50%)" },
          "100%": { transform: "translateY(0)" },
        },
      },
    },

